1.  Intro


2.  Building

2.1  Building from git source

    If you are building from the git sources, then you will need to build the
autoconf scripts. Since MLib needs shared libraries, the process involves
libtool:

    $ cd mlib.git/
    $ libtoolize
    $ autoreconf
    $ ./configure # etc, etc
